    "is_free": true,
    "description": "400年后，地球已不复存在，人类在星际间找到了新的家园。争夺太空中的一席之地，留下了内乱和残酷派系战争的遗产。银河系被10个交战派系所瓜分，每个派系都有自己的议程。例如，“永生之子”不惜一切代价追求永生，而MPL则以利润为目标，天朝则通过庞大的间谍网络打击腐败。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深渊</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/ffdd7727e40085c499a52e0b5df0f9b9.poster.avif?t=1764066428\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/ffdd7727e40085c499a52e0b5df0f9b9.webm?t=1764066428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/ffdd7727e40085c499a52e0b5df0f9b9.mp4?t=1764066428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>“深渊”突然出现，引发了边境的混乱。作为指挥官，你的最终目标是揭开深渊的秘密，并防止它吞噬一切。这个充满探索元素的游戏模式让你选择道路并做出关键指挥决策，决定你的奖励。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏模式与挑战</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/f7d7abca1f27af9bc0d31c3b58512028.poster.avif?t=1764066428\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/f7d7abca1f27af9bc0d31c3b58512028.webm?t=1764066428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/f7d7abca1f27af9bc0d31c3b58512028.mp4?t=1764066428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>PvE内容: 享受丰富剧情的战役并挑战艰难的赏金任务。<br>PvP竞技场: 在战略性太空战斗中与其他玩家一较高下。<br>宝库: 加入联盟并突袭宝库以获取宝贵资源。<br>深渊: 揭示秘密，在这个以探索为重点的模式中做出关键决策。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >招募独特的飞行员</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/effba78702cda91dee9fb278bd7f2d07.poster.avif?t=1764066428\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/effba78702cda91dee9fb278bd7f2d07.webm?t=1764066428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/effba78702cda91dee9fb278bd7f2d07.mp4?t=1764066428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>收集超过100艘飞船，每艘飞船都有独特的能力和背景故事。通过强力升级改造你的舰队和飞行员，统治太空。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深度定制</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/32f17f780af6bcaa2b6fe75cd9616341.poster.avif?t=1764066428\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/32f17f780af6bcaa2b6fe75cd9616341.webm?t=1764066428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/32f17f780af6bcaa2b6fe75cd9616341.mp4?t=1764066428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>通过各种武器、护盾和软件来自定义你的飞船。利用多达6个装备槽，并收集强力植入物，打造无限可能。根据你的战略需求和战斗偏好量身定制舰队。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握你的战术</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/ebb6a14733278744e62f3b7583d916f0.poster.avif?t=1764066428\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/ebb6a14733278744e62f3b7583d916f0.webm?t=1764066428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/ebb6a14733278744e62f3b7583d916f0.mp4?t=1764066428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>使用策略战术击败强大的敌人，逐步成为传奇指挥官。仔细规划你的行动，创造完美的舰队组合，并根据飞船的独特攻击模式选择编队，以最大化战斗效果。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >限时活动</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/230d32ca5bf91a99e01376bff6882457.poster.avif?t=1764066428\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/230d32ca5bf91a99e01376bff6882457.webm?t=1764066428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/230d32ca5bf91a99e01376bff6882457.mp4?t=1764066428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>参与激动人心的活动和节日主题悬赏任务。参加社区挑战，并在指挥官街机游戏中体验迷你游戏，如《未来幸存者》。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索银河</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/effba78702cda91dee9fb278bd7f2d07.poster.avif?t=1764066428\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/effba78702cda91dee9fb278bd7f2d07.webm?t=1764066428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021540/extras/effba78702cda91dee9fb278bd7f2d07.mp4?t=1764066428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在《星辰边境：前线》中，广袤的银河是你的战场。运用策略和战术在科幻宇宙中航行，征服挑战，在星际间建立你的传奇。感受战略太空战斗的刺激，指挥舰队进行科幻冒险。掌握战略艺术，沉浸在一个由你选择决定银河命运的科幻史诗中。参与战略规划和科幻战斗，成为《星辰边境：前线》的终极指挥官。在这个科幻宇宙中，每个方面都需要策略，而你的战术决策将决定你的成功。",
